1 SECTION 2. AMENDMENT. Section 12-47-18.1 of the North Dakota Century Code is
2 amended and reenacted as follows:
3 12-47-18.1. Transfer of persons between correctional facilities.
4 TheSubject to statutory limitations, the director of the department of corrections and
5 rehabilitation may transfer an offender to any facility under the department's control or contract
6 to transfer an offender to another correctional facility for purposes of safety, security, discipline,
7 or medical care, or when the director determines it may be in the best interests of the public, the
8 offender, or the department.
